						<p><hi rend="bold">King: ⎯⎯ Year: ⎯⎯</hi></p>						

						<p>In characters of the tenth century A.D. This damaged hero-stone records the death of king Pṛithuvipati probably of the Gaṅga lineage. This also seems to register a certain grant whose details are not clear.</p>						

